data.description: Nestled in Clearlake's Northfork Subdivision, this one-story gem boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a study. Situated on a cul-de-sac lot beside walking trails, the home welcomes you with an elegant entryway, soaring ceilings, and ceramic tile floors complemented by custom columns. The living room features a cathedral ceiling and a custom slate-finished fireplace, with a study tucked behind French double doors.  The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, offering an island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, abundant natural light, and custom tile backsplash and built-ins. The owner's retreat is generously spacious, featuring vaulted ceilings, double vanities, custom built-ins, a large walk-in custom shower, and an expansive walk-in closet.  Recent updates by the seller include a remodeled primary bathroom in 2019, recent AC and ductwork in 2021, and a hot water heater replacement in 2021.   Home Warranty provided by the seller. Call for a private tour today!
